    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ear ornaments in the form of studs, frequently with decorative elements, worn through a hole pierced in the lobe of the ear.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
